The chalet is three stories with two fully equipped units that can sleep up to 18 people. The upper two floors of the cabin consist of three bedrooms, 2 baths, a fully equipped kitchen, and great room. There is a large deck off the main level where you will find the hot tub. The master bedroom also resides on the main level and includes a king size bed and a set of twin bunk beds. The bath is in the hall as well as the stairway leading to the lower unit and utility room which includes a washer, dryer and a ski tuning area. The great room includes a table that seats up to 14, a glass front wood stove, Dish TV, VCR/DVD (movie library included), and a stereo.

The lower level is a one bedroom, one bath living space that has been newly remodeled. The kitchen is fully equipped and has a small dinette area that seats 4 around a small maple table. The living area contains an entertainment center, complete with TV and VCR/DVD (movies only). The large bedroom sleeps 4 in one king and one set of bunk beds.  A wood stove, in the main living area, keeps you cozy on the coldest of days and a fresh supply of seasoned wood is just outside your door. The house offers DSL internet as well for those who need to stay connected while they are away, thought note that streaming might be a little slow.

