Located about 13 miles from Mt. Hood's Skibowl, 19 miles from Timberline, and 24 miles from Mt. Hood Meadows, this gorgeous mountain retreat is the perfect rental for skiers and riders in the winter, and hikers and bikers in the summertime. And at just under 44 miles from Portland, guests will be close to urban delights as well!

Groups of up to 15 guests can rent the entire Lodge at Welches. For a more intimate setting, a couple may rent the  Welches studio.

Impressive in size and stature, this expansive lodge sits in a quiet neighborhood. Its elegant, lightly-vintage mountain decor keeps the entire group cozy, whether socializing together as one large group, in smaller groups, or having alone time. This home's amenities include WiFi, cable, and DVD players for entertainment. There's also a two-car garage for convenience.

The incredible great room, with its vaulted ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking the back deck and Foxglove Golf Course, is the perfect place to gather as a group before the roaring fireplace. Spread out onto the deck for a cookout, cocktails, or a soak in the hot tub.

