This studio, and the larger home which is also available for bigger parties, are part of the Resort at the Mountain. There's two golf courses, a full-service spa, fitness center, croquet and lawn bowling court, sand volleyball and badminton courts, children's playground, and outdoor pool (enclosed and heated seasonally).

This beautiful home is located right near the Salmon/Huckleberry Wilderness where you can explore 31 miles of trails, including the popular, Salmon Creek Trail. Anglers can toss their lines in the nearby Sandy, or head over to the Salmon River. If you're coming in winter, Skibowl and Summit are about 15 minutes to the east. Mount Hood Meadows is about 45 minutes away.

