When you're not loafing around this beautiful Brightwood vacation home, check out the Timber Rim Rec Center for swimming and fitness, drive 20 minutes to Mt. Hood Skibowl for alpine sports, and the surrounding area for Nordic skiing and snowshoeing trails. Visit Little Crater Lake 50 minutes away for hiking and camping, or trek to Mirror Lake at the base of Mt. Hood, just a 20-minute drive from the house! Need a city fix? Take an hour drive to Portland!

One thing is sure, your next mountain adventure starts at this wonderful Mt. Hood vacation rental!

