This charming vacation rental chalet is an end unit, so you'll have a little extra privacy. Though it's conveniently close to the pool, the laughter and voices from hot tub won't disturb you. This is a great space with lots of amenities; a perfect spot to just sit and read a book or work on the laptop (Free WIFI). Slip one of the DVDs you brought along into the player and watch a movie. Catch the latest episode of your favorite series on the cable TV. Or, head over to the Creekside clubhouse. There, you can burn off some calories in the heated pool (heated decks surround it to melt the snow in the winter), lounge in the hot tub or sauna, or read that book in front of the grand, floor to ceiling fireplace as the wood fire crackles and pops!

