With timber beams, an earth-toned interior, and the surrounding forest, this abode is truly your own cabin in the woods!

You'll sink right into comfort in the spacious living room - with a gorgeous native rug next to the stone, wood-burning fireplace, plus an L-shaped couch and arm chairs, there's tons of room for everyone in your group to lay back and relax! Play board games on the floor or crowd around the flatscreen TV in the corner to catch your favorite flicks on the DVD player. You'll also have WiFi so you can stay in touch and check your email if needed.

