For the skiers and snowboarders in your group, the fantastic slopes of Timberline and Mt. Hood Meadows are within a 20-mile drive - an easy commute right up Highway 26! Work your muscles on the slopes, or pack your mountain biking gear and pedal your way around the resorts, there are tons of activity options at these resorts all year round.

