There are so many options for day trips surrounding this home - the Columbia River Gorge is only an hour away and is famous for its windsurfing and kite surfing, plus there's Hood River, which is an awesome mountain town with several breweries and shopping worth checking out.

Whether you're trying to organize a big reunion for your family, a retreat for your business, or a vacation for your friends, this beautiful Mt. Hood vacation rental will keep everyone relaxed and entertained up in the wilderness!

