Collins Lake is a lovely option for Government Camp lodging: the rentals offer two or three bedrooms (select units are even pet-friendly) and a triple-level floor plan that includes a private, heated garage on the lower level, a gas fireplace in the living room,  and WiFi throughout. During your stay in Government Camp, visit the resort's clubhouse and warm yourself in front of the stone fireplace. There's also a year-round outdoor pool and hot tub - perfect for playing or relaxing after a day on the slopes! Or, if you prefer, hit the sauna for some vacation rejuvenation. Just be sure to bring your ski gear - there are no less than four ski resorts within a few minute's drive - Mt. Hood Meadows, Mt. Hood Skibowl, Timberline, and Summit Ski Area.

