The full kitchen is centrally located right near the dining room and living rooms, so you can socialize or carry on conversations while sitting in front of the fire or while getting dinner ready. There's an island cooktop, refrigerator, oven, and dishwasher at this charming Fairy Ring Cottage. And when it's time to eat, gather everyone around the wooden table on the edge of the kitchen. On sunny summer evenings, eat dinner out on the deck and admire the tree-lined view. There's even an outdoor grill if you have a craving for some barbecued chicken thighs.

