Beer connoisseurs, outdoor enthusiasts, and families alike will love this three-bedroom Sunriver vacation rental with a private hot tub, gas fireplace, and resort amenities like trails and SHARC for eight lucky guests! 14 Lark is a woodsy retreat in the heart of Central Oregon, and the ideal year-round vacation and reunion spot!

The home is located at Sunriver Resort in the beautiful Deschutes National Forest, a playground of sorts for hikers, mountain bikers, and paddle sports enthusiasts along the Deschutes River! Learn about the starry night sky at the Oregon Observatory (two miles away), ski black diamonds at Mt. Bachelor (16 miles), or launch your boat at the Sunriver Marina on opening fishing day. Come snowfall or sunshine, this home is at the heart of adventure!

Enjoy complimentary passes to the state-of-the-art SHARC aquatics center or explore your sleepy neighborhood by bicycle. The garage offers plenty of space for all your outdoor gear. Inside, there's wonderful rustic outdoor decor and cozy amenities. Snuggle up on the leather sectional or play a family boardgame. Warm your toes by the gas fire, or gather for media entertainment including three cable TVs, a VHS library, and WiFi so you'll never catch cabin fever!

Gather for hearty meals around the wood dining table with seating for eight or dine outdoors. Everything tastes better on the grill! Eat outdoors on the platform patio surrounded by trees, or make way to the enclosed back deck offering a glass-top table and umbrella with seating for six.

The kitchen features a breakfast bar with two additional seats and modern appliances to host a Fourth of July feast or chili cook-off on a cold winter day. Additional home amenities like a dishwasher, as well as a washer and dryer for your clothes will keep clean-up to a minimum while you're on vacation!

This fantastic two-story home boasts two downstairs bedrooms, and one upstairs, with a bonus room, two full baths, and one half bath for up to eight guests. Guests will sleep easy on a king bed, two queen beds, a full bed, and one twin bed. The bedrooms are cozy with great natural lighting and plaid and outdoor themed decor. Two suites offer private patio access and the upstairs bonus room features a pyramid bunk and a second living room!

Watch a throwback movie from the VHS library or play a game of foosball. Upstairs grants access two two fantastic tree-top decks. Bring on the morning with a steaming cup of coffee or count shooting stars as a family at night.

Outside, relax in the rocking chair with a glass of wine or soak in your private hot tub! Shoot hoops in the driveway or walk to Sunriver's Fort Rock Park offering tennis courts, volleyball, baseball, basketball, horseshoes, and a playground!

Sample a flight of beer at the Sunriver Brewing Company right in the Village at Sunriver or pick up a cheesy slice at Blondie's Pizza. Follow the Trail to Benham Falls for unbeatable views or schedule a mountain biking excursion with The Paulina Plunge. Sunriver Resort also offers four championship golf courses, multi-use trails, horse stables, and more!

Whether exploring the outdoors or lounging at home, this charming Central Oregon vacation rental offers all the convenience (plus some extra fun) of home!

