This classic, comfortable Sunriver vacation home is located off Ponderosa, and is located right on the bike path, which offers quick access to paved bike trail system that traverses the area. The house features five adult bikes and two children's bikes for an easy ride to the newly renovated Village at Sunriver. The Village is filled with restaurants, shops and even our local ice cream and candy store. You're also minutes away from SHARC, the fabulous new aquatic center with pools, play areas, a year-round tubing hill and much more. You receive six free passes to SHARC for your stay.

