If you're looking for a comfortable place to enjoy an excitement-filled Central Oregon trip, this Sunriver vacation rental might be the perfect place. Featuring all the comforts of home, space for seven to eight guests, and easy access to everything the resort community of Sunriver has to offer, everyone will have a wonderful time here!

Conveniently located in the center of Sunriver, within about a mile of the SHARC, restaurants, and the lodge and Village Mall, when you stay here you will have easy access to everything in the community. You will also be 25 minutes from downtown Bend, and just 30 minutes from skiing at Mt. Bachelor, as well as wonderful hiking, biking, and all the other opportunities Central Oregon offers.

With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home has just enough space for eight guests. Have a seat in the living room on the cabin-style sofas, and watch some cable TV, use the DVD player, or simply sit back and turn on the fireplace to keep the home extra cozy. In the home you will also have two more TVs, as well as DVD players, WiFi access, and even a laundry room that will come in handy in case anyone's clothes get a little dirty while exploring the area.

Just past the living room, a full kitchen has just about everything you may need to whip up tasty meals during your stay. With all major appliances (even a dishwasher for easy cleanup), you will have no trouble cooking up anything from a simple breakfast of pancakes and eggs to a full Sunday roast dinner! Sit down together at the dining room table and enjoy a family-style meal together before heading out for the day.

This main level also has the master bedroom, which features a king-size bed where you will sleep soundly and rest up for another day of vacationing. This main floor also has a full bathroom. If you head upstairs, you will find two more bedrooms and another full bathroom, as well as a loft area. One of these bedrooms has a cozy queen-size bed, the other room contains a twin-over-full bunk bed, and the loft features a twin bed with a twin trundle underneath.

Outside, you will have a gas grill and a patio area, so you can cook up a tasty meal and enjoy the fresh air. Within the condo complex you have access to a seasonal shared pool, as well, which can make pool time anytime with its close proximity! In Sunriver you can access the fantastic SHARC aquatic center, which has indoor and outdoor pools, water slides, a hot tub, and outdoor sport courts and recreation areas.

Elsewhere at the resort you will have no shortage of fun activities to keep busy (some activities may require a fee). While you're here you can visit the tennis courts, work out in the fitness center, book a tee time on one of the golf courses, walk around the 30 miles of paved trails, or take a guided horseback ride around the scenic nearby area. You could also go rafting or fishing on the nearby Deschutes River, mountain biking or hiking in the Deschutes National Forest, or even drive (or take the free shuttle) just 30 minutes up to Mt. Bachelor for some wintertime skiing, snowboarding, or sledding adventures!

At Sunriver Resort you will find several eateries, shops, and a market where you can stock up on groceries, though you may want to drive into wonderful Bend for even more options. The charming downtown area is just a 25-minute drive from this vacation home, so don't be afraid to take the short trip into town to peruse the shops, museums, galleries, and other attractions there. Bend is also famous for its breweries, so you can stop at any of them, including the especially well-loved Deschutes Brewery for a pint and a particularly tasty burger. However you spend your vacation, you will surely find excitement in every direction!

Bring your family or friends to this comfortable, spacious, and conveniently located Central Oregon vacation rental and enjoy all the amenities and adventures that Sunriver Resort has to offer!

