The unit is located in Skyline Condos as part of the Sunriver Resort community. Skyline Condos includes full resort access – including shared pools and hot tubs at the SHARC – and a shared hot tub for condo guests. This 13 Skyline retreat is conveniently located near the Deschutes River, horse stables and nature center!

The two-story condo is bright and open with a welcoming floor plan ideal for entertaining. The woodsy decor and solid wood furniture will inspire your outdoor adventures! Snuggle up on cold nights around the gas fireplace or watch flicks on the flatscreen cable TV. You can even pack your little one's favorite DVDs from home!

The spacious living room offers seating for the whole family and is adjacent to the kitchen. Grab a quick breakfast at the bar for two or serve a holiday feast around the formal table for six. The kitchen features ample counter space and modern appliances to make meal prep a breeze.

Family barbeques are best served outdoors! The private patio boasts a gas grill, lounge chairs, and a bistro table so you can serve grilled hamburgers and fresh lemonade.

With three bedrooms and two full baths, 13 Skyline comfortably sleeps six guests. Bedrooms are minimalist yet elegant with large windows and storage options. Downstairs offers a bedroom with two twin beds. Upstairs, one bedroom features a king bed and a second bedroom offers a queen bed. Extra amenities like WiFi, and a private washer/dryer will make guests feel right at home.

