Back inside, you'll have three bedrooms at night for catching a good night's sleep. The master has a king-size bed and a beautiful view of the trees, while another bedroom upstairs has another king bed, as well as a twin-size trundle bed. And downstairs, the remaining bedroom has a twin bed - perfect for an older child.  You'll also have one-and-a-half bathrooms at 11 Raccoon.

If you do choose to bring up to two dogs with you, it's just a small nightly fee.

Sunriver Resort is one of the most popular, family-friendly destination resorts in all of Central Oregon! Right near the base of the Cascade Mountains, with paved trails, tennis courts, horse stables, pools, hot tubs, and recreation centers, there's always something to do here. There are four specially-designed golf courses,  including Caldera Links, a nine-hole course that's great for the whole family. You'll also find restaurants and shopping at Sunriver Village.

In winter, Mt. Bachelor is only 30 minutes away and right at Sunriver Lodge, you can catch a shuttle (for a nominal fee) to and from the slopes, if you don't feel like making the short drive yourself.

