This spacious Sunriver vacation home has amazing outdoor decks, a private hot tub, and a fantastic location near Fort Rock Park and the Woodlands Golf Course! Perfect for sunbathers in the summer and skiers in the winter, the home is a wonderful year-round destination.

With 2,100 square feet of living space spread across three floors, there is plenty of room for up to eight guests to share this sun-drenched home. The main living areas are on the middle floor, with beautiful windows overlooking the pine trees in the yard and skylights set into the beautiful exposed-timber ceilings. On chilly evenings, a large gas fireplace surrounded by leather sofas is the perfect spot to relax and watch a movie on the cable TV with DVD player.

The great room also has a large dining table for six (with plenty of space for extra chairs), perfect for sitting down to a special holiday meal. For casual occasions, the fully-equipped kitchen has a bar with two stools and overlooks a breakfast nook with seating for four. On the south side of the home, a sunroom with cozy chairs will beckon bookworms, and the desk with computer provides a nice home office for those who need to stay connected while away.

On the first floor, a master suite has a queen bed and private attached bath. There is a large open room that can be used for a second living space (with its gas fireplace and TV) or as an extra bedroom, since it has both a double bed and a twin. This floor also has a second full bath.

Up on the third floor is a delightfully cozy queen bedroom for one lucky couple, with a sliding glass door leading out to a private deck.

The south side of the house has a sunny barbecue area with a private hot tub, and outdoors lovers will adore this getaway. The spacious decks, proximity to Fort Rock Park and Sunriver's fantastic bike paths, and tree-lined yard will keep any family busy on pleasant summer days. In the winter, the cozy mountain decor and space for up to eight guests makes it a fantastic ski getaway! And, of course, your stay includes eight unlimited, complimentary passes to SHARC (the resort's lavish aquatic center).

