ay and reset the machine and on we went.  After all had happened, I must say that, although I was not happy about them not answering calls, but Vacasa immediately fixed the problem-  they answer the call immediately after all that had happened.  Obviously they care about their business and I am happy with that.  They are trying to do things right.  Internet breaking down was not their fault but I had a feeling that they would do better in the future in informing their customers what to do.  I respect people who is willing to correct their mistakes and make their customers happy.

