After your hours of fun, you'll appreciate the comforts of this reverse living home, recently upgraded with new carpeting. Relax in the great room with its vaulted ceiling, large windows and wood-burning fireplace - and head for the connecting the kitchen to prepare your meals. You can eat in the dining area with its large table, or step out onto the deck to barbecue your meals and enjoy them outdoors. Don't miss a soak in the hot tub to end up each day.

Upstairs, you'll find the master bedroom with a queen bed, a handsome bathroom and a powder room. Downstairs, there are two bedrooms - a bunkroom with three sets of twin bunk beds, and another bedroom with a queen and a twin. A hall bath plus a washer and dryer round out the conveniences on the ground floor.

14 Cherrywood is a prime place for family and friends to relax, but when you're ready for action, it also offers easy access to Highway 97 and nearby Bend. Enjoy the "big city" for nightlife, dining and retail therapy, and then come back to your Sunriver retreat.

