This classic Sunriver home has it all - a charming rustic interior, completely updated amenities and location, location, location!

3 Pinecone is just steps away from the finest recreation and vacation treats in the area. You can play on top-rated golf courses within minutes, or take a bike trail to the marina for kayaking or canoeing. It's a short stroll to Sunriver Village where you can shop and dine, and you're also close to SHARC, the exciting new aquatic center. (Guests at 3 Pinecone get 10 unlimited passes to the new center.)

This fabulous house in the woods is ideal for large family gatherings, your golf buddies or a group of girlfriends. Downstairs, the kitchen is well stocked for entertaining--it even has two refrigerators to hold all your food and drink. In warm weather, you can entertain and barbecue on the deck and patio that open to a forested common area. In winter, everyone may gather around the fabulous wood-burning fireplace in the comfortable great room, watch movies on the flat screen TV or warm up in the large hot tub outside.

This house sleeps a crowd, with two bedrooms downstairs, each featuring king beds. On the same floor, you'll find a bath with a luxury Jacuzzi tub and separate shower.

Upstairs there's a loft that's open to the great room below. This space has a couch, chairs, a TV and a card table, so it's a great spot for teenagers to hang out or for another generation to play a wild game of pinochle.

Also, upstairs you'll discover four more charming bedrooms and a full bath with shower. One bedroom has a queen bed; one has twin bunk beds that kids - or anyone - will enjoy; and two bedrooms have two twin beds each. With space for up to 10 guests, and a pet-friendly attitude (please note that a $10 nightly, per-pet fee with a $40 minimum per stay applies), everyone will have a great time!

You'll fall in love with this home - and so will your pets. It's animal friendly, and two- and four-footed guests can all use the walking paths literally outside the door. Don't miss this charmer filled with rustic hospitality!

