Guests will appreciate the authentic woodland feel of this home, while enjoying tasteful modern highlights such as the spiral staircase, updated kitchen interior, colorful accent walls, and private hot tub!

Upon entrance you'll be welcomed by wood beam vaulted ceilings, a well-lit interior and comfortable country style design. Slip off your shoes to enjoy the plush carpet and warm yourselves in front of the wood burning fireplace after a long day of winter play. Spend and evening at home piled on the beautiful red leather sofas or recliner seat for a movie night in front of the flat screen TV.

