When it's time for bed you'll be lulled to sleep by soft comforters, charming patterns and fluffy pillows in each room. The lower level bedroom has a kingsize bed, plenty of closet storage, flat screen TV and a large window looking out onto the deck. Head upstairs via the wrought-iron spiral staircase and you'll find a warmly lit private bedroom with a double bed and roof line post beam ceiling. Mosey into the loft area with two twin beds and TV for extra sleeping and lounge space. Traveling families or groups of up to six will appreciate the private yet dynamic layout of bedrooms and sleeping options available.

Make sure to plan time for the outdoors, as this house features a large back patio space with a private hot tub, gas grill and outdoor seating. Further completing the unbeatable value of the Antelope 11, the owners have included six SHARC passes! And don't worry, travel necessities have not been skipped: this home comes complete with WiFi, cable TV, two parking spaces, and a stacking washer/dryer combo.

Take the family for a full day of adventure with a rafting trip down the rapids of the Deschuttes, or keep things warm in the winter with a tour of the High Desert Museum. Hit Mt. Bachelor for supreme skiing, snowboarding and snowshoeing, or wander off the beaten path to Smith Rock State Park for epic rock climbing and hiking. When you've worked up a thirst make sure not to miss the awesome beer flight specials from Deschutes Brewery downtown! For those with a taste for urban entertainment make sure to plan a few hours to explore the Old Mill District, filled with upscale shops and boutiques, restaurants, a movie theatre and summer concert series!

Whether it's the mountains, desert, snow or the river that brings your group to Sunriver, you'll be happy to call this two bedroom house with a loft your home during your travels. Perfect for up to six people with its flexible sleeping spaces, multi-level arrangement and large patio space, you'll be planning the next Central Oregon getaway before you've even left.

