The open floor plan here means socializing is easy whether some in your group are in the living room, the kitchen, or even sitting at the dining table. And when it is time to prepare meals, the bright full kitchen has all the major appliances you'll need to make tasty vacation meals, as well as a dishwasher to make clean-ups easier. Use the breakfast bar for cereal in the morning, or as a spot to open up your laptop and use the WiFi to check your email.

