Nestled in the north end of Sunriver, this home is just across the street from a beautiful golf course and is only a few steps from a bike trail that circles around the community. Because this house is on the edge of the resort, you will enjoy a quieter atmosphere, while still only being a short drive to all of the resort's amenities.

When you step inside this house, you will be greeted by warm colors, wood details, and colorful artwork on the walls that welcome you to your temporary home. The main living area, on the upper floor, is a warm and cozy space with lots of windows that offer views of the trees surrounding the property.

The living room has comfortable seating arranged around the lovely gas fireplace. A large flat screen TV equipped with cable and a DVD player, plus Internet access, family-friendly board games, and books are also available, so everyone will have plenty of entertainment choices.

A gorgeous full kitchen will delight anyone who loves to cook. Fully appointed with stainless steel appliances and all the equipment you may need to prepare meals during your stay, cooking in this spotless, spacious kitchen will be fun! Enjoy your homemade meals while sitting at the breakfast bar, or at the sturdy dining room table while looking out at the scenery.

