Outside, you will find an inviting deck with plenty of patio furniture for everyone to sit and breathe in the fresh air. A gas grill provides a great opportunity to cook outside and enjoy the nice weather. Best of all, a private hot tub is just waiting for you to soak in its warm, bubbling water and enjoy some true relaxation.

Within the community of Sunriver, you will have so many activities and amenities available to you. 10 free SHARC passes come with this home, so head to the magnificent aquatic center to enjoy the shared pools, hot tubs, sports courts, and other offerings! In the area you will also find four golf courses, horseback riding, spa, fitness center, and hiking and biking trails.

With the Deschutes River so close, whitewater rafting, kayaking, and fishing are also popular pastimes. Nearby you will also have access to several eateries, shops, and a market. However, with Bend so close (about a 25-minute drive), you could easily drive into town for a pint at any of the fabulous breweries, a visit to a museum, some shopping, and a nice meal at one of the many amazing restaurants.

