This Central Oregon vacation rental is close to a number of activities - boating on the Deschutes River (there's even room for boat parking and RVs in the driveway), a day spent hiking or biking along the Deschutes National Forest trail, or you can borrow the four kids bikes and ride around the neighborhood.

