You'll truly feel like you've arrived at your own cabin at the edge of the wildernesss when you enter this charming, traditionally decorated home. Comfortable furniture surrounds a flat screen TV, and a wood beamed ceiling extends far up above your head. Settle in for the night to watch cable, read a book, surf the Web, or play a board game - whichever you choose, you'll be nice and cozy here!

