Other amenities include a washer and dryer, stereo, CD player, WiFi, gas grill, and central air conditioning. You'll have all the comforts of home at this high desert getaway!

Situated on a quiet cul de sac, you'll be right near the Deschutes River, Woodlands Golf Course, and miles of well-kept, scenic, hiking and biking trails. This home comes with unlimited use Sunriver Homeowners Aquatic & Recreation Center (SHARC) passes so everyone in your group can swim in the outdoor/indoor pools, play in the lazy river, and fly down the water slide to their heart's content.

Other attractions at this popular Central Oregon resort include Deschutes River float trips at the Sunriver Marina, three award-winning golf courses (as well as a family-friendly, nine-hole course), restaurants, shops, and winter activities such as nearby snowshoeing and cross-country skiing. You can even catch a shuttle at the Sunriver Lodge (for a small fee) to Mt. Bachelor Ski Resort for a day of downhill skiing and snowboarding!

