Adventure seekers will feel right at home in Bend. There is whitewater rafting on the Deschutes River which runs right through town, lots of hiking trails throughout the Deschutes National Forest, as well as mountain biking and rock climbing spots nearby. Of course, Mt. Bachelor is only about 20 miles west, so skiing and snowboarding are certainly an option in the winter months.

