The Skyliner condo itself is well-laid out and has the best balcony for enjoying evening barbecues or a moment of early morning relaxation while enjoying a cup of green tea. The living room has a comfortable leather futon that turns into a queen-sized mattress for extra sleeping space, a flat-screen television with cable, fireplace, and a stylish chair you can settle into with a good book. There's even WiFi so you can keep up with work back home, if you must.

Off of the living room is a little eating space where you can enjoy a home-cooked breakfast or a late night came of cards. The kitchen may seem small, but it has just about everything you'd need to be chef! This compact kitchen has a full-sized stove, microwave, dishwasher, and a refrigerator off to the side. Go ahead and pack the supplies for a vegetable lasagna, because you'll be able to prepare and cook it here.

This Central oregon vacation rental has one bedroom with a king sized bed. The lucky occupants in this room will love sinking into this big comfortable bed while enjoying the morning sun trickling through the sliding glass doors. You may even decide to wander out onto the balcony for some fresh air. This room has its own full bathroom with bathtub/shower combo, and there is an additional full bath in this apartment so all four guests will never feel too rushed to abandon their long, hot shower. This home also comes equipped with a washer and dryer. No vacation is complete without your four-legged friends! Well-behaved dogs are welcome in this pet-friendly home, although please note that there is an additional nightly fee of $10 per pet ($40 minimum per stay).

Surrounded by green parks and the beautiful Deschutes River, you'll wonder why you didn't decide to visit Bend sooner! This is a walkable town, so take your time wandering around the various parks, crossing the pedestrian bridge to see what's on the other side, or checking out the eclectic tastes of Bend's eateries. Walk to the Bend Brewing Company to see what's on tap or head to Zydeco Kitchen & Cocktails for an Old Fashioned. On the way, maybe you'll see something else that excites your taste buds.

Book the Skyliner today for your next ski, shopping, or hiking getaway, and you will love having your own stylish condo to call home for a few days in the heart of Bend!

