Relax on the spacious front porch with a glass of iced tea or wine in the afternoons - chances are the Central Oregon weather will be nice and sunny! But when you do spend time indoors, the downstairs living room is a peaceful, comfortable spot to read a book, or borrow a board game from the shelf and spread it out to play.

