Located just west of Redmond, Oregon, Eagle Crest offers over 1700 acres full of activities including sports centers, golf courses, and hiking trails - all against the backdrop of the gorgeous Cascade Mountain Range. A stay at this resort also puts you close to the western-themed town of Sisters (16 miles away), busting Bend (17 miles away), and outdoor attractions like Smith Rock State Park (15 miles northwest) for hiking and rock climbing. And in winter, both Hoodoo Ski Area and Mt. Bachelor Ski Resort are within a 45-minute drive.

